additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Irritating to eyes and skin. Keep out of the reach of children & pets. Avoid contact with the skin and eyes. Wear suitable gloves. May cause an allergic reaction in some individuals. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water and seek medical advice. After contact with skin wash immediately with soap and water. If swallowed seek medical advice immediately and show this container or label.
